            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-11/file7nm8v4t4yf4mtw23nsx_0.jpg?VersionId=qxZ2WhqMnsuYWkFpizfwRz3OF.gKHwcI&amp;itok=MGrlTYml" title="美国总统拜登在与中国国家主席习近平会晤后召开记者会说，中美无须进入新冷战。（法新社）" alt="美国总统拜登在与中国国家主席习近平会晤后召开记者会说，中美无须进入新冷战。（法新社）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-11/file7nm8v4t4yf4mtw23nsx_0.jpg?VersionId=qxZ2WhqMnsuYWkFpizfwRz3OF.gKHwcI&amp;itok=MGrlTYml" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
